        <h2>Brochure</h2>

        <p>If you would like to receive a copy of our programme through the post then please let us know your address by emailing <a href="mailto:info@starandshadow.org.uk?subject=Brochure">info@starandshadow.org.uk</a>.</p>

        <h2>Email Lists</h2>

        <p>If you would like to receive information by email you can sign up to some of our mailing lists.  The main lists are:</p>

        <!--
        <h4>Announce</h4>

        <p>For announcements to cinema members and other interested people about screenings, gigs and other events at the cinema.</p>
        -->

        <h4>Volunteers</h4>

        <p>To send messages to cinema volunteers about work going on at the cinema, and for organising work shifts.</p>

        <form class="form-inline" method="post" action="http://www.simplelists.com/subscribe.php">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="sr-only" for="input_name_">Name</label>
